rs. Chopra’s compelling tale, encompassing three distinct regions of the British Atlantic, will be read by scholars across a range of fields.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 27. Jan 2023) 0aMaroonszJamaicaxHistory. 0aMaroonszNova ScotiaxHistory. 0aMaroonszSierra LeonexHistory. 7aHISTORY / Modern / 18th Century.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2018z978311063899840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300235227423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300235227/original  a978-3-11-063899-8  Yale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2018b2018  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-UCY